r />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,等同明確承認開分身 R730(狗隻#137604)<br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"7e9198babe4680482932d3b22d007f75c1df1dee","tid":2252350,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acf2d6a7cb5553d664f2fd05c56f947ed34e7ffa","tid":2252350,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bf30b469c0df33c651a900b4c439197a2949cb63","tid":2252350,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T16:31:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-la